reviews.name: Arm & Hammer 9-Pack Odor Eliminating Vacuum Bags, Eureka RR ™ Premium Allergen
reviews.reviewText: I had to laugh when they arrived, I know exactly what must have happened to earlier reviewers. YES there are 3 packages in the box. There are 3 bags in each package. I can only assume some of the other reviewers saw 3 packages and assumed each held one bag. My order was site to store and it arrived as promised. A great value compared to picking them up off the shelf in the physical store.
reviews.title: Let's count them!

reviews.name: Arm & Hammer 9-Pack Odor Eliminating Vacuum Bags, Eureka RR ™ Premium Allergen
reviews.reviewText: Love these premium bags...they really do help contain the fine dust particles better. The 9-bag-bundle (3 packages of three bags each) is a really good deal. I paid $6 for the last 3-bag pack I bought.
reviews.title: Premium Allergen Bags ARE Better
